#
#   [X.Y.Z] ([YYYY-MM-DD]) - [Brief description of changes]
#
# # Purpose & Function
#
# Purpose: Define environment-specific configuration and secrets
#
# Core Design: KEY=VALUE pairs loaded at runtime
#
# Key Features:
#
#   - Application configuration (ports, URLs, feature flags)
#   - Database connection strings
#   - API keys and secrets (NEVER commit real values!)
#   - Service URLs for external integrations
